window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After our recent victory against Queen Titania’s forces, I thought my harem and I would get some time to relax.</b></p> <p>Maybe throw a few parties in my subspace and invite the finest from the Celestial and Infernal Academies. Turns out that the Beast of Revelation is on the loose, and it wants to eat the entire universe, starting with Hell itself.</p> <p>Someone needs to defeat the beast and put it back in its cage. And the Prince of Darkness has come to me for help.</p> <p>I’ve made my home in multiple realms, with women from each of them, and I’m not about to let anyone ruin what I’ve built. Even if it’s the Beast itself.</p>"; 
